    <name>
      <text>Leaders</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<h1><strong>Leaders in Array</strong></h1>
<p>Write a program that finds all leaders in an array of integers.</p>
<p>An element is considered a leader if it is greater than all the elements to its right.</p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong></p>
<p>[16, 17, 4, 3, 5, 2]</p>
<p><strong>Output:</strong></p>
<p>[17, 5, 2]</p>]]></text>
